            &lt;p&gt;Here&amp;rsquo;s the situation: It&amp;rsquo;s game 3 of a sealed game. You know your opponent has &lt;a class=&#34;cardname&#34; href=&#34;http://gatherer.wizards.com/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;type=card&amp;name=Mind%20Control&#34; target=&#34;_new&#34;&gt;Mind Control&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a class=&#34;cardname&#34; href=&#34;http://gatherer.wizards.com/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;type=card&amp;name=Aether%20Adept&#34; target=&#34;_new&#34;&gt;Aether Adept&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a class=&#34;cardname&#34; href=&#34;http://gatherer.wizards.com/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;type=card&amp;name=Plummet&#34; target=&#34;_new&#34;&gt;Plummet&lt;/a&gt; still in his deck, so you should finish it quickly to avoid losing to topdecks.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The field is as shown (click for larger view):&lt;/p&gt;











