&lt;p&gt;If you Stampede and swing with everyone, you win! Unless he has &lt;a class=&#34;cardname&#34; href=&#34;http://gatherer.wizards.com/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;type=card&amp;name=Condemn&#34; target=&#34;_new&#34;&gt;Condemn&lt;/a&gt;, in which case you will lose. You never saw &lt;a class=&#34;cardname&#34; href=&#34;http://gatherer.wizards.com/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;type=card&amp;name=Condemn&#34; target=&#34;_new&#34;&gt;Condemn&lt;/a&gt; in previous games. If you swing with everyone except &lt;a class=&#34;cardname&#34; href=&#34;http://gatherer.wizards.com/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;type=card&amp;name=Platinum%20Angel&#34; target=&#34;_new&#34;&gt;Platinum Angel&lt;/a&gt; he will fall to one life and you have to find a way to push through the extra damage later.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;What&amp;rsquo;s the correct play?&lt;/p&gt;



